{"tid":1585278,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"崔天凱 斥 香港分裂者 成「民族罪人」","createTime":"2019-09-21T14:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T19:22:44.000Z","uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e73c9a13a9da8ba6240255d357e762e66d66de19","tid":1585278,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/5c13504e817c6f094baeb7f825a3d09a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F5c13504e817c6f094baeb7f825a3d09a&h=247010f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n崔天凱指出，香港亂下去對誰都沒有好處。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/bcf6dfed9189376faa58f9e81b95e632\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fbcf6dfed9189376faa58f9e81b95e632&h=d60c7adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n約二十人昨午手持美國國旗在港大校園遊行。（港大學生會學苑即時新聞Fb）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港反對修訂《逃犯條例》風波已擾攘逾三月，仍未有平息迹象。中國駐美國大使崔天凱昨於華盛頓表示，「利莫大於治，害莫大於亂」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港亂下去對誰都沒有好處，分裂者將成民族罪人。</span></strong>他警告任何勢力不要低估中國貫徹一國兩制、維護香港繁榮穩定的堅定決心。<br />\n<br />\n崔天凱在使館的十一活動儀式上致詞，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">指某些勢力在香港假自由、民主之名，行違法暴力之實，甚至妄圖通過搞亂香港動搖一國兩制根基</span></strong>，這種圖謀是徒勞的，絕不會得逞。他強調，自由、民主從來不是、更不應被當作暴力違法的贖罪券。鄧小平在四十年前已指出，統一是全國各族人民的共同願望和中國的國家意志，誰膽敢將香港分裂出去，必將背上民族罪人的千古罵名。<br />\n<br />\n崔天凱又稱，一國兩制是完整概念，其中<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一國是根本，根深才能葉茂</span></strong>，本固才能枝榮。他表示，中國面對挑戰，必堅決鬥爭，並取得勝利。"},{"pid":"2717d78c21e9b75d200b8454573de87a6e54a0bc","tid":1585278,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:00:37.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/崔天凱斥分裂者成民族罪人-214500629.html\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%B4%94%E5%A4%A9%E5%87%B1%E6%96%A5%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E8%80%85%E6%88%90%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E7%BD%AA%E4%BA%BA-214500629.html&h=fba5b6e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9eb8c0087c72d2598ee068e686842ddec33979a5","tid":1585278,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:01:26.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/崔天凱斥分裂者成民族罪人-214500629.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%B4%94%E5%A4%A9%E5%87%B1%E6%96%A5%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E8%80%85%E6%88%90%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E7%BD%AA%E4%BA%BA-214500629.html&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYobsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=bbb06aee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/崔天凱斥分裂者成民族罪人-214500629.html</a>"},{"pid":"6b1e99db9ceaf380e054d0c4e4e01826e3c33515","tid":1585278,"uid":294555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:02:30.000Z","msg":"係咪驚攬炒啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02a90f6ea57759721a5106ad4e5020bd866989c","tid":1585278,"uid":70336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"邊個嚟 唔L識<br />\n街邊藍絲使L理佢"},{"pid":"ea34e36e15c58348c5df654095190ccf5a93db68","tid":1585278,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:03:34.000Z","msg":"Who.gif"},{"pid":"54bbe2bfdcecf051a0a66737cfab95160a08d69e","tid":1585278,"uid":250721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"冇人得到好處就啱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225d3845fa4f6bd3211faae752dc202350ff3862","tid":1585278,"uid":151525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"當敵人群起反對你的時候"},{"pid":"046b8b55d65e888bc71feddc7403f9796c31667f","tid":1585278,"uid":256059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"支那成日都係咁, 成日講到自己所向無敵乜撚都唔驚, 下一句就話人搞死你成咩民族罪人千古罪人"},{"pid":"59a17ae2b587f44ebd2af64b39c1d51e56ecbbc2","tid":1585278,"uid":322775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl